<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P0962: Pressure Control Solenoid “A” Control Circuit Low
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Measured circuit current of line pressure control solenoid valve is lower than limit due to short to ground, even if command circuit current for line pressure control solenoid valve is within specification.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(1 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" morerows = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Solenoid valve (CVT assembly) and/or its circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Valve body assembly (CVT assembly)
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
TCM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P0966: Pressure Control Solenoid “B” Control Circuit Low
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Measured circuit current of primary pressure control solenoid valve is lower than limit due to short to ground, even if command circuit current for primary pressure control solenoid valve is within specification.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(1 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P0970: Pressure Control Solenoid “C” Control Circuit Low
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Measured circuit current of low brake control solenoid valve is lower than limit due to short to ground, even if command circuit current for low brake control solenoid valve is within specification.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(1 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P2720: Pressure Control Solenoid “D” Control Circuit Low
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Measured circuit current for high clutch &#38; reverse brake control solenoid valve is lower than limit due to short to ground, even if command circuit current for high clutch &#38; reverse brake control solenoid valve is within specification.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(1 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P2764: Torque Converter Clutch Pressure Control Solenoid Control Circuit Low
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Measured circuit current for TCC (Torque Converter Clutch) solenoid valve is lower than limit due to short to ground, even if command circuit current for TCC (Torque Converter Clutch) solenoid valve is within specification.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
(1 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</servinfosub>
