</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Check that the following condition is satisfied in this procedure.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
11 V &#60; Battery voltage &#60; 15 V
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Set ignition ON.
</ptxt>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENCP70A5504034004">
<title>
DTC Troubleshooting
</title>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
This DTC Troubleshooting explains the inspection for P0962: Pressure Control Solenoid “A” Control Circuit Low. For P0966, P0970, P2720, and P2764, perform the same inspection.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<diag type = "test" id = "AENCP70A5504034005">
<testgroup id = "AENCP70A5504034006">
<question>
Was “CVT System Check” performed?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 2.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to 
<intxref refid = "AENCP70A5504001">CVT System Check</intxref>
.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENCP70A5504034007">
<title>
Line pressure control solenoid valve check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
With ignition OFF, disconnect “C142” connector. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5506028"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check line pressure control solenoid valve. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5506029"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
 
</ptxt>
</test1>
<question>
Is it in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Go to Step 3.
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Replace line pressure control solenoid valve (CVT assembly). 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5506017"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
<testgroup id = "AENCP70A5504034008">
<title>
Line pressure control solenoid valve drive circuit check
</title>
<test1>
<ptxt>
With ignition OFF, disconnect “C09” and “E19” connectors.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
Check for proper terminal connection to “C09” and “E19” connectors.
</ptxt>
</test1>
<test1>
<ptxt>
If connections are OK, check the following point.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Resistance between “A2” circuit and ground: infinity
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</test1>
<question>
Is it in good condition?
</question>
<result type = "yes"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Substitute a known-good TCM and recheck DTC. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "AENCP70A5506004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</action>
<result type = "no"/>
<action>
<ptxt>
Repair or replace defective wire harness.
</ptxt>
</action>
</testgroup>
</diag>
